item.title: Dave Clark Five - Do You Love Me - Key of C
item.description:
As performed by the Dave Clark Five
Transposed to the Key of C
Video contains directions for music classroom use. Call and Response style playing. Chords used: C F G
This revision fixes an issue with a couple of chords placed on the wrong lyric. I do not own the copyright to this music.
